entity.dragonminez.saga_raditz.line1: » §6Raditz§f › Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha. Impressive. You actually managed to singe some of my leg hair.
entity.dragonminez.saga_raditz.line2: » §6Raditz§f › So you wanna die? Fine, I'll be happy to oblige.
entity.dragonminez.saga_raditz.die_line: » §6Raditz§f › My Saiyan comrades will avenge me... The two of them, I know they will... In one year, they will come... And when they do, you will pay for what you did to me...
entity.dragonminez.saga_nappa.line1: » §6Nappa§f › Vegeta, what does the scouter say about his power level?
entity.dragonminez.saga_nappa.line2: » §6Nappa§f › You're pissing me off, low-class loser!
entity.dragonminez.saga_nappa.die_line: » §9Vegeta§f › Nappa no longer has any use to me. Goodbye, HAAAA!
entity.dragonminez.saga_vegetasaiyan.lin: » §9Vegeta§f › I am the prince of all Saiyans, the prideful elite warrior, Vegeta!
» §9Vegeta§f › You're a fool! I'm going to teach you the meaning of pain!
entity.dragonminez.saga_vegetaozaru.line: » §9Vegeta§f › HAHAHAHA, YOU'RE NOT A RIVAL FOR ME!
» §9Vegeta§f › I'M THE STRONGEST WARRIOR IN THE UNIVERSE!

stats.dmz.level.desc: §7Calculated by the sum of all your stats, divided by 5. The more level you are, the more powerful you are.

stats.dmz.tps.desc: §7You can get more TPs by §chitting §7enemies or §ckilling §7enemies. You can get even more TPs in the §bHyperbolic Time Chamber§7.

stats.dmz.def.desc: §7Reduces the damage you take from enemies.
stats.dmz.con.desc: §7Increases your health points. Also increases your Stamina.
stats.dmz.pwr.desc: §7Increases your Ki Damage. At more damage, more Ki you will spend.
stats.dmz.tpc: §9Training Points Cost§7: The cost to increase your stats.
stats.dmz.tpc.desc: §7You can also increase how much you want to increase your stats.
stats.dmz.ki_damage: §9Ki Damage: §7The damage you deal to enemies with your Ki Attacks.

dmz.ccreation.human.description: They are a terrestrial race with highly versatile combat skills. While they lack the innate power of other races, they are incredibly resourceful and tenacious. They stand out for their perseverance and courage, able to overcome their limitations through training and discipline.
dmz.ccreation.saiyan.description: They are a warrior race born for combat. Their innate ability to grow stronger after each battle makes them formidable opponents. They can even transform into powerful Super Saiyans and take their abilities to unimaginable levels.
dmz.ccreation.namek.description: They are a peaceful yet powerful race, with great regenerative abilities and a natural connection to magic and nature. They are known for their wisdom, energy control, and their ability to fuse with others of their kind, increasing their power.
dmz.ccreation.bioandroid.description: They are artificially created beings, combining the DNA of the most powerful races. With the ability to absorb other beings and increase their power to unimaginable levels, these creatures are adaptable and dangerous, designed to be invincible.
dmz.ccreation.colddemon.description: They are a race of intergalactic conquerors with immense power and boundless cruelty. Their ability to transform and increase their power makes them formidable enemies. Despite their fragile appearance, they are some of the deadliest creatures in the universe.
dmz.ccreation.majin.description: They are a magical and unpredictable race with enormous destructive potential, with a unique ability to regenerate and change form. Though they may seem playful or childish, they are extremely dangerous when they unleash their true power.

dmz.skill.meditation.name: Meditation
dmz.skill.meditation.desc: Boosts your Passive Ki Regeneration and Stamina Recovery; Also reduces the Ki Cost of the Turbo Boost.
dmz.skill.ki_control.name: Ki Control
dmz.skill.ki_control.desc: Learn to Control your Ki. It's a basic skill to use Ki Attacks.
dmz.skill.ki_manipulation.name: Ki Manipulation
dmz.skill.ki_manipulation.desc: Master the Ki Manipulation to be able to create Ki Weapons, increasing your Melee Damage based on your Ki Damage!

dmz.skill.passive.desc.saiyan: §fSurvive 6 seconds below §b10%%§f HP to §bheal §b%d%%§b HP §fand §bboost your stats by §b%d%%§f. You have §b%d Zenkais left§f, remaining cooldown: %dm %ds§f.
dmz.skill.passive.desc.bio: §fIf you are below §b50%%§f HP, you §bheal §b%d%%§f of base damage dealt. If below §b25%%§f HP, you §bheal §b%d%%§f.

lines.master_korin.menu: Hmm... I see you’ve made it up to my tower. Not many do. What are you looking for, young one?
lines.master_korin.nube: Hrm... I see, you want the famous Flying Nimbus. I can give it to you, only if you prove you have a pure heart.
lines.master_korin.senzubeans: Senzu Beans? I have a few left, these are the last ones!
lines.dende.menu: Hello there! I am Dende, the actual Guardian of Earth after Kami. Anything I can help you with today?
lines.dende.reset: So you wanna start over? I can reset your character for you.
lines.dende.heal: You look hurt. Let me heal you...
lines.shenron.menu: I am Shenron, the Dragon God of Earth. I shall grant you one wish. What is your desire?
lines.shenron.capstr: Do you want Red Capsules? They grant you +5 STR stat points each.
lines.shenron.capdef: Do you want Purple Capsules? They grant you +5 DEF stat points each.
lines.shenron.capcon: Do you want Green Capsules? They grant you +5 CON stat points each.
lines.shenron.capene: Do you want Blue Capsules? They grant you +5 ENE stat points each.
lines.shenron.capkipw: Do you want Orange Capsules? They grant you +5 KiPOW stat points each.
lines.shenron.senzu: Senzu Beans are the Master Korin specialty. I can give you some of them.
lines.shenron.radar: This piece of technology will help you find the Namekian Dragon Balls.
lines.shenron.revive: So you want to come back to life... I can do that for you.
lines.shenron.revive_other: You want to revive someone else? Fine, but you can only revive three people.
lines.shenron.revive_others_chat: » §2Shenron§f › Type the Exact Nickname for those you want to revive, separated by commas. [Nick], [Nick], [Nick].
lines.shenron.revive.revived: » §2Shenron§f › You have been revived by §b%s§f. Talk to King Yemma to come back to the living world.
lines.shenron.revive.fail: » §2Shenron§f › You can not revive §b%s§f, either is not dead or is not in the server.
lines.porunga.menu: I am Porunga, the Dragon God of Namek. I shall grant you three wishes. What is your desire?
lines.porunga.menu_sec: You have two more wishes. What do you want?
lines.porunga.menu_trd: You have one last wish. Anything else?
lines.porunga.senzu: Senzu Beans are a Magic Bean that heals you completely. I can give you some of them.
lines.porunga.gete: Gete... The Big Star left a lot of debris on Namek... What a disaster...
lines.porunga.revive_other: You want to revive someone else? Fine, but you can only revive three people, but it will take all your wishes.
lines.porunga.revive_others_chat: » §2Porunga§f › Type the Exact Nickname for those you want to revive, separated by commas. [Nick], [Nick], [Nick].
lines.porunga.revive.revived: » §2Porunga§f › You have been revived by §b%s§f. Talk to King Yemma to come back to the living world.
lines.porunga.revive.fail: » §2Porunga§f › You can not revive §b%s§f, either is not dead or is not in the server.
lines.master_goku.menu: Hey, it's me, Goku! What can I do for you? Do you want to train with me?
lines.master_goku.dialogue: You look strong! I can teach you a few things. Why don't you train with me? I'll make you stronger!
lines.master_kaio.menu: Hehehe, first you have to tell me a joke. If it's good, I'll train you, hehehe!
lines.master_kaio.dialogue: HAHAHAHA, that was a good one! You're funny! I'll train you, hahaha!
lines.master_roshi.menu: Oh, I didn't see you there! Have you seen my magazines? I can't find them anywhere! I need them for... research purposes.
lines.master_roshi.dialogue: Yeah... They're yoga magazines! I need them to... stretch my muscles! Yeah, that's it... Not for anything else...
lines.elder_guru.menu.evil: You're not §7*cough*§r welcome here... Evil one... Please §7*cough*§r leave this place....
lines.elder_guru.menu.human: Hello, Earthling. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.menu.saiyan: Hello, Saiyan. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.menu.namekian: Hello, my son. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.menu.bio: Hello, Bio-Android. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.menu.colddemon: Hello, Cold Demon. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.menu.majin: Hello, Majin. §7*cough*§r I am the oldest Namekian alive. §7*cough*§r The Grand Elder Guru... I can see you have a pure heart... §7*cough*§r Do you want something from me?
lines.elder_guru.potunlock.fail: You need to §7*cough*§r let your potential grow... §7*cough*§r before I can unlock it...
lines.elder_guru.potunlock.success: I can unlock your true potential... §7*cough*§r You are now stronger than before... I hope you use it §7*cough*§r for good...
lines.elder_guru.potunlock.max: You have already unlocked your potential... §7*cough*§r I can't do more for you this time...
lines.elder_guru.heal: You look hurt... §7*cough*§r Let me heal you...
lines.enma.menu: Welcome, mortal. I am the King Yemma, this is my Check-In Station for the Other World. If you want to go back to the living world, you need to ask me.
lines.enma.talk: You want to go back to the living world? I can send you back, but you need to be alive first. Talk to Baba, she can help you, she's in the left side.
lines.enma.revive: Are you sure you want to go back? You'll have to die again to come back here.
lines.enma.norevive: You can't go back to the living world if you're not alive. Talk to Baba first.
lines.baba.menu: Hello, I am Baba, the fortune teller. I can see your future... Do you want me to tell you something?
lines.baba.talk: I can see you want to go back to the living world... I can help you, but only for a temporary time... Are you ready?
lines.baba.revive: Are you sure you want to revive temporarily? You'll have to summon Shenron to revive yourself, if you can't do it, you'll come back here.
lines.baba.norevive: You have to wait %s to temporarily revive again.
